label("$C$", V + W, SE, fontsize(10));
label("$G$", U + V + W, NE, fontsize(10));
[/asy]

Compute
\[\frac{AG^2 + BH^2 + CE^2 + DF^2}{AB^2 + AD^2 + AE^2}.\]

